	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Aspiring Mage,<BR>
<BR>
I play on the Rallos Zek server.  I too am a Newbie mage, and newbie to the game.  I use the second F10 option which is the fullscreen view with the windows.  It shows 10 slots for hotkeys, although you can still program 10 hotkeys in the main view mode as well.<BR>
<BR>
Malacites are found in cities everywhere, and on some jewlers around Norrath.  They cost about 6 sp each.  I usually buy 4 stacks of 20 at a time and they last quite a while.<BR>
<BR>
Being a mage and with your low level pets not being summoned &quot;warlords&quot; just yet, you'll die quite a few times, but fear not, the mage class is extremely fun to play.  Learn your pet commands early and use them well.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
